(null, 'news', 'Performance Counters are missing.', 'Run FAR, press Alt-Space  and  select  "Properties"  item  to  open properties  of  FAR console window,  select "General"  and  uncheck "QuickEdit mode"  option.  Then  press  Enter  and  select "Save properties for future windows with same title".', 'pic3.jpg', 'http://yandex.ru', 1, 1, '2010-10-25 11:20:05', 1, '2010-10-25 11:20:05', '2010-10-25', '2010-11-02', 10),
